  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The current version supports Gamepad and change keys! And easy mode!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/b352f54e09740e298f39511a079cb052.avif?t=1649728645\" width=600 height=113 /></span><br>What will happen if you were a beautiful princess and you got kidnapped into the abyss by a <br>monster just to get rid of your fiancé? <br>That is what happened to her, she was only 15 years, she was able to call her fiancé for help <br>but she chose to prove she is not weak, and from that moment her journey to get out of the <br>abyss start. Move between lands Fight Enemies and bosses <br>What?!! <br>Revolution!! <br>king of the abyss is sealed in a prison!! <br>a new king appeared!! <br>Discover who sealed the old king? and what is going on in the abyss? <br>Can she get out of the abyss by herself?? <br>Who is her fiancé?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/3d3629b2c0f57ee79f854021685bc26c.avif?t=1649728645\" width=600 height=113 /></span><br>● The horizontal jumping action of the hard core, it may not be easier than Celeste at all.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/edfd06a593290e202c544a1833f2ee2f.avif?t=1649728645\" width=600 height=113 /></span><br>● The Game featuring new Attack System Gameplay by using Dash and Attack at same <br>time <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/69d463a4003b17a34f5cfcc5acffdd6d.poster.avif?t=1649728645\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/69d463a4003b17a34f5cfcc5acffdd6d.webm?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/69d463a4003b17a34f5cfcc5acffdd6d.mp4?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>● Using dash will make you invisible for little time to avoid any Damage while touching <br>tarps or Attacking enemies <br><br>● Pixel art side-scrolling action, with a new modern visual style. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/4a0e03171a60a3b885765714c45fd17c.poster.avif?t=1649728645\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/4a0e03171a60a3b885765714c45fd17c.webm?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/4a0e03171a60a3b885765714c45fd17c.mp4?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>● Tightly tuned 2D controls. dash, run, jump, and slash your way through even the most <br>deadly Enemies. <br><br>● Explore many Different Lands Lava Land, Green Land, Trap Land, Bomb Land, Shadow <br>Land, etc. that contain many different areas. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/902d3304746e7cf0c1bf036ad6435633.poster.avif?t=1649728645\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/902d3304746e7cf0c1bf036ad6435633.webm?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791650/extras/902d3304746e7cf0c1bf036ad6435633.mp4?t=1649728645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video 